text: "I Don't Want To" is a song by American singer Ashley Monroe. ==Music video== It premiered on CMT on October 5, 2006. The video debuted at number 20 on CMT's Top 20 Countdown for the week of November 9, 2006. The music video reached number 1 on CMT's Top Twenty Countdown for the week of February 15, 2007. ==References== Category:2006 songs
